scopecontent.p:
The collection consists of material created by and relating to Lee Wilson Dodd, documenting his career as a playwright and author of fiction. The bulk of the collection consists of drafts and circulating versions of playscripts and other writings by Dodd (including a draft of a single novel, 
               Mouse
            ). Also included are two folders of correspondence, one folder of playbills, and one folder of photographic negatives.
